[
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks to work by <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-email=\"vaidaplankyte@gmail.com\" data-user-id=\"1906\">@Vaida Plankyte</span>, we've added a ton of new title-texts that try to teach the user keyboard shortcuts they may not know about. For example, hover your mouse over the Drafts button. <br>\nFeedback/bugs/ideas for improvement much appreciated!</p>",
        "id": 272670,
        "sender_full_name": "Rishi Gupta",
        "timestamp": 1503535327
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>One is that the hotkey hints in the popovers don't feel like they are obviously hotkey hints. Maybe they could be styled differently from the rest of the text (e.g. be grayed out)? Or be right justified?</p>",
        "id": 272672,
        "sender_full_name": "Rishi Gupta",
        "timestamp": 1503535503
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>i believe the default <code>title</code> popovers do not support styling, so we'd probably have to move to JQuery/Bootstrap tooltips if we want extra styling. I agree it takes a few encounters with the current popovers to realise what they mean</p>",
        "id": 272785,
        "sender_full_name": "Vaida Plankyte",
        "timestamp": 1503562521
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Though there seems to be \"tricks\" to use CSS-only for the popovers, not sure how this works out in terms of greying out a part of them.<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.ecoconsulting.co.uk/examples/css-tooltip/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://www.ecoconsulting.co.uk/examples/css-tooltip/\">http://www.ecoconsulting.co.uk/examples/css-tooltip/</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/484137/is-it-possible-to-format-an-html-tooltip-title-attribute\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/484137/is-it-possible-to-format-an-html-tooltip-title-attribute\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/484137/is-it-possible-to-format-an-html-tooltip-title-attribute</a></p>",
        "id": 272786,
        "sender_full_name": "Vaida Plankyte",
        "timestamp": 1503562710
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>just to clarify, by popovers here I meant these:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/2c/w4wxnX5WQek5jw-U_71jBi5t/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">pasted image</a> <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/94/Ro3F8COjLj9fPZBCFP8h4pDs/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">pasted image</a> <a href=\"/user_uploads/2/41/DF1R7whf4XKLCB9GwFRTMzoZ/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">pasted image</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/2c/w4wxnX5WQek5jw-U_71jBi5t/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted image\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/2c/w4wxnX5WQek5jw-U_71jBi5t/pasted_image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/94/Ro3F8COjLj9fPZBCFP8h4pDs/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted image\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/94/Ro3F8COjLj9fPZBCFP8h4pDs/pasted_image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/41/DF1R7whf4XKLCB9GwFRTMzoZ/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted image\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/41/DF1R7whf4XKLCB9GwFRTMzoZ/pasted_image.png\"></a></div>",
